Class ChatEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cuni.mff.kocur.world.ChatEvent

  • public class ChatEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that represents a ChatEvent. This class stores the chat's message, id of player that sent the message and if the message is meant only for the team.

    kocur
